Start a Whatsapp Web chat conversation without hassle. 

Feature:

1. Direct message whatsapp number without the need to save the number to contact list. You can open chat message for unsaved number on WA web, this extension will make contacting with a single-time phone number easier. 

Mesej Je originally is an Android business tools app for Whatsapp (WA) users and now has come to Chrome Extension! For full functionality kindly download Mesej Je at Playstore.

Mesej Je relied on the official WA to verify a phone number, depending on your internet connection and refresh list you might experience an error "number not register" once in a while.
